'''哈迪·巴赫拉'''（{{lang-ar|'''هادي البحرة'''}}，{{bd|1959年|1月1日|||catIdx=B}}）<ref name="NCS1">{{cite web|url=http://en.etilaf.org/coalition-components/general-body/political-committee/other-political-body/hadi-al-bahra.html|title=Hadi Al Bahra|publisher=National Coalition for Syrian Revolutionary and Opposition Forces|accessdate=13 August 2014|language=en|archive-date=2015-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150521143003/http://en.etilaf.org/coalition-components/general-body/political-committee/other-political-body/hadi-al-bahra.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>是前[[叙利亚反对派和革命力量全国联盟|叙利亚反对派和革命力量全国联盟]]主席，曾是叙利亚反对派领导人之一。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/07/syrian-opposition-body-elects-new-president-2014793458830884.html|title=Syrian opposition body elects new president|work=Reuters|date=9 July 2014|accessdate=14 August 2014|language=en|archive-date=2015-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150207143435/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/07/syrian-opposition-body-elects-new-president-2014793458830884.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>之前，他担任叙利亚和谈的驻瑞士日内瓦首席谈判代表。<ref name="Reuters1">{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/09/us-syria-crisis-opposition-idUSKBN0FE08120140709|title=Syria's Western-backed opposition elects new president|last=Theiler|first=Mike|date=9 July 2014|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=13 August 2014|language=en|archive-date=2014-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007011910/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/07/09/us-syria-crisis-opposition-idUSKBN0FE08120140709|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2014年7月9日，巴赫拉以62票当选[[叙利亚反对派和革命力量全国联盟|叙利亚反对派和革命力量全国联盟]]主席，击败41票的莫法奇·内拉比亚。<ref name="Reuters1" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syrian-opposition-elects-hadi-al-bahra-as-new-leader.aspx?pageID=238&nID=68869&NewsCatID=352|title=Syrian opposition elects Hadi al-Bahra as new leader|date=9 July 2014|work=Agence France-Presse|publisher=Hurriyet Daily News|accessdate=13 August 2014|location=Istanbul|language=en|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006104258/http://www.hurriyetdailynews.com/syrian-opposition-elects-hadi-al-bahra-as-new-leader.aspx?pageID=238&nID=68869&NewsCatID=352|dead-url=no}}</ref>

